name: A Look is the Strongest Fist

metadata.name: A Look is the Strongest Fist
metadata.description:
If there is something more powerful than a thousand punches, it is a look. In this analog photo I will call you beyond boxing and punches. Because you cannot beat emotions, emotions are above all physical blows. So is a look. Sometimes it breaks silence, sometimes it mobilizes an army. Sometimes a look expresses only sadness, sometimes a look is poetry. But in the end, a look is stronger than all blows and punches.

The eyes always win.

Camera: Yashica Fx3 Super 2000  
Film: Fujifilm Fujicolor c200
